{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/7-gaya-paling-enak-buat-baca-komik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"7 Gaya Paling Enak Buat Baca Komik","content":"<p>Artikel ini bakal bagiin 7 gaya paling enak buat baca komik. Enjoy, bro sis!</p>\n<p>Di era yang udah serba digital kayak sekarang, hampir semua aktivitas pake perangkat digital. Hampir semua orang udah pake <em>smartphone, tablet, </em>dan <em>gadget</em> canggih lainnya. Buat apa? Buat <em>chatting, </em>belanja <em>online, </em>bersosialisasi lewat <em>social media, </em>dan masih banyak lagi. Begitu pula dengan baca komik. Tapi gaya apa ya yang paling enak buat baca komik digital? Langsung aja yuk pantengin 7 gaya berikut.</p>\n<p><strong>1.Tiduran</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1827\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1827\" data-attachment-id=\"1827\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/7-gaya-paling-enak-buat-baca-komik/attachment/content-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"content-7\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1827\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-7.jpg\" alt=\"(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1827\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Leyeh-leyeh abis pulang kuliah ato kerja, udah lelah seharian, langsung aja ya kan baca komik favorit sambil tiduran. Saking keenakan, jangan sampe lupa mandi ato ganti baju ya. Hehe…</p>\n<p><strong>2. Tengkurap</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1828\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1828\" data-attachment-id=\"1828\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/7-gaya-paling-enak-buat-baca-komik/attachment/content-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"content-6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1828\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-6.jpg\" alt=\"(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1828\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tengkurap disinyalir sebagai salah satu gaya dasar yoga. Dengan posisi bhujangasana, bro sis bisa melenyapkan lemak yang menumpuk di perut. Posisi yoga yang satu ini juga cocok untuk kelenturan bagian pinggang dan tulang belakang loh. Bahkan dengan rutin melakukan bhujangasana, bro sis bisa terhindar dari yang namanya sakit punggung. (Nape jadi bahas gerakan yoga yak? :p ) Nah, kalo baca komik sambil tengkurap, bisa sambil latian gerakan-gerakan yoga juga kan bro sis. Pikiran di-<em>refresh </em>sama cerita-cerita komik yang kece, badan juga fit. Mantap kan tuh, dapet 2 <em>benefit </em>sekaligus.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Di Kereta</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1829\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1829\" data-attachment-id=\"1829\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/7-gaya-paling-enak-buat-baca-komik/attachment/bodyyy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bodyyy.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"bodyyy\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bodyyy-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bodyyy.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1829\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bodyyy.jpg\" alt=\"(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bodyyy.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bodyyy-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1829\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Baca komik digital emang paling praktis dilakuin di mana aja. Bahkan lagi di kereta pun, bro sis bisa ngelakuinnya dengan bebas karena tinggal buka <em>handphone </em>nya aja, komik-komik yang udah ditungguin seminggu bisa kamu baca. Selain kepo sama jalan ceritanya, baca komik di kereta juga bisa nge-<em>refresh </em>pikiran kamu. Para pejuang kereta pasti udah terbiasa ngerasain <em>umpek-umpekan, </em>desek-desekan, bahkan menghirup berbagai aroma semriwing. Baca komik di kereta bisa jadi pelipur lara di kala pegel ato nunggu sampe di stasiun tujuan.</p>\n<p><strong>4. Berdiri Nunggu Kereta</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1830\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1830\" data-attachment-id=\"1830\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/7-gaya-paling-enak-buat-baca-komik/attachment/content-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"content-5\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1830\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-5.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: static.pexels.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1830\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: static.pexels.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Di mana-mana, yang namanya nunggu pasti bikin bosen. Biar nunggu nggak jadi hal yang menjengkelkan lagi, bro sis bisa sambil baca komik. Berdiri nunggu kereta pun nggak akan se-ngebosenin itu. Tapi kalo nunggu gebetan nembak, bisa nggak ya sambil baca komik? Eeeeiiittsss… (Awas baper!)</p>\n<p><strong>5. Berdiri di Transjakarta</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1831\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1831\" data-attachment-id=\"1831\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/7-gaya-paling-enak-buat-baca-komik/attachment/content-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"content-3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1831\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-3.jpg\" alt=\"(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1831\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Buat para pejuang TJ (baca: Transjakarta), pegel karena berdiri dalam waktu yang lama mah udah biasa. Tapi pegelnya nggak bakal kerasa kalo sambil baca komik. Bisa ketawa-ketiwi baca komik komedi, termehek-mehek baca komik romantis terpopuler, ato tegang baca komik <em>action. </em></p>\n<p><strong>6. Di Bawah Meja</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1832\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1832\" data-attachment-id=\"1832\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/7-gaya-paling-enak-buat-baca-komik/attachment/content-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"content-1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1832\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-1.jpg\" alt=\"(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1832\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Inget waktu jaman ujian, bro sis ada yang suka nyontek di bawah meja nggak? Udah nggak jaman! Sekarang jamannya baca komik di bawah meja. Tangan kanan masih sibuk kerja, tangan kiri bisa megang <em>gadget </em>biar nggak ketinggalan komik-komik favorit bro sis. Sambil menyelam, minum air lah ya…</p>\n<p><strong>7. Keroyokan</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1833\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1833\" data-attachment-id=\"1833\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/7-gaya-paling-enak-buat-baca-komik/attachment/content-4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"content-4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1833\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-4.jpg\" alt=\"(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/content-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1833\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Dokumentasi CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Nah, satu lagi gaya yang juga patut dicoba. Keroyokan! Iya, keroyokan. Bukan keroyokan berantem ya…Tapi keroyokan buat baca komik terbaru gitu kayaknya nih. Baca bareng-bareng gitu maksudnya.</p>\n<p>So, gaya mana yang menurut bro sis paling enak buat baca komik? Up to you, guys…</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"4caed990-7e29-5a85-9aa1-84d992e93246"}}}